cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.CL, cs.CV

The paper discusses the limitations of standard deep learning approaches and proposes a new approach to overcome these limitations. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE) sub-categories. The paper also discusses sequence prediction problems, which suggests that it may belong to the natural language processing (cs.CL) and computer vision (cs.CV) sub-categories.
